data.description: 123 Millwood Way, in Millwood Estates, Bardstown, is a captivating All-Brick Ranch with an open and inviting layout. The kitchen has abundant cabinets, a spacious 6-foot island, and ample counter space. The expansive living room, featuring vaulted ceilings, serves as a welcoming space for gatherings and cherished moments. The master suite provides a luxurious retreat, with a spacious bedroom, a soothing soaking tub, double vanity, and a convenient walk-in closet. The spa-like master bath ensures relaxation and convenience. The property spans over .72 acres, enclosed by a new privacy fence for utmost seclusion. The covered back deck is perfect for outdoor living, while inside, new flooring adds a modern touch. A separate brick outbuilding with electric service offers endless possibilities More...as a workshop, studio, or additional storage space. Additional Storage in attic, above the garage using the pull down ladder. Meticulously maintained and beautifully landscaped, this home offers a harmonious blend of serenity and convenience, being close to amenities, schools, and recreational options. Don't miss the opportunity to make 123 Millwood Way your new home.
